{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "e8796bbc-5fe9-4d64-8b63-3d7a3b57f859", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/e8796bbc-5fe9-4d64-8b63-3d7a3b57f859@3.pkg/1772597584612/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597585543", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/e8796bbc-5fe9-4d64-8b63-3d7a3b57f859@3.pkg/1772597584612/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597585543"}, "identifier": "e8796bbc-5fe9-4d64-8b63-3d7a3b57f859", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>题文中，“围炉夜话”的民主形式，拓宽了民主渠道，丰富了民主形式，有利于增强村民的民主参与意识，有利于保障村民的知情权和表达权，①④正确；“满足村民的全部诉求”的说法夸大了“围炉夜话”的作用，②错误；村民的民主权利是宪法和法律赋予的，不能随意扩大，③错误。</p>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<p>瓦屋山下，龙苍沟里。一处农家院坝内，一炉篝火烧得正旺，龙苍沟镇干部和村民们围坐在一起，围绕产业发展、村民增收、用好政策等话题，热络地“说事、解疑、答惑”。这种充满烟火气的“围炉夜话”，有利于（ &nbsp;&nbsp;）</p>\n\n<p>①增强村民的民主参与意识　 ②倾听并满足村民的全部诉求　</p>\n\n<p>③扩大村民享有的民主权利　 ④保障村民的知情权和表达权</p>\n", "title": "瓦屋山下，龙苍沟里。一处农家院坝内，一炉篝火烧得正旺，龙苍沟镇干部和村民们围坐在一起，围绕产业发展、村民增收、用好政策等话题，热络地“说事、解疑、答惑”。这种充满烟火气的“围炉夜话”，有利于（   ）①增强村民的民主参与意识　 ②倾听并满足村民的全部诉求　③扩大村民享有的民主权利　 ④保障村民的知情权和表达权", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["B"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/e8796bbc-5fe9-4d64-8b63-3d7a3b57f859@3.pkg/item.json?v=1754670059611", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "children": [